plotRank = function(GROUP){
  x.string=GROUP
  df = data %>%
    group_by_(GROUP) %>%
    summarise(n = n()) %>%
    arrange(-n) %>%
    top_n(20)
  p = ggplot(df,aes_string(x=x.string,y='n'))
  p + geom_bar(stat='identity') + coord_flip()
}
